						               													<description>The captain has vanished and now it is time for you to squabble for the leadership of our boat! Are you ready to share one of you Huge Deed in the high sea to win this dispute?!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mar de Mentiras is a party game for 3 to 7 players, where the pirates struggle to get the crew support to become the new captain of the ship! Share one of your Huge Deed to impress the crowd and watch out not to loose everything to a Hairy Hearsay!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first pirate to get the support of 15 crew member will become the new captain! Be ready to mislead your friends with your stories and know the right moment to share your Darkest Secrets about your enemies. And the most important thing: try not to get caught sharing a Tell Tale.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every turn a Pirate will tell a story from a selection of 3 possible story cards. All other pirates will discuss if they believe this story or if anybody wants to challenge, but beware, crew members hate when you challenge a true story and you will loose their support, else if you catch a liar you will steal some of it's crew members support to yourself.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play story cards, tell some tales, get support of 15 crew members and become the new captain.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
